Why Does Your Neck Hurt?
It’s not just “sleeping wrong.” Here are 3 common culprits:

1. Poor Posture
Slouching, scrolling, and screen time strain your spine.

2. Nutrient Deficiencies
Low magnesium or B vitamins = muscle tension and fatigue.

3. Chronic Stress
Stress lives in your shoulders — and your nervous system.

We help gently unwind the patterns causing your pain so you can feel better from the inside out.
